    <BIBL>

        <TITLE>Passions- und Oster-Predigten</TITLE>
        <FORMAT>4to</FORMAT>
        <PRICE currency="fl.">2</PRICE>
    </BIBL>

        <PRICE>fl. 1. 30. kr.</PRICE>
    </BIBL>
    <BIBL>

        <TITLE>Nouvelle Grammaire Francoise & Allemande</TITLE>
        <FORMAT>8vo</FORMAT>
        <PRICE unit="kr.">32</PRICE>
    </BIBL>

    </BIBL>

        <PRICE unit="kr.">40</PRICE>
    </BIBL>
</ITEM>","number_of_corrections":9,"explanation":"1) Added NOTE element for introductory free text. 2) Removed garbled characters (\u221a, \u2020, mis-encoded “√ü”). 3) Corrected mis-encoded German letters in three titles. 4) Replaced unmatched <PRICE>/<PRIZE> pair and harmonised all price tags to <PRICE>. 5) Escaped ampersands to &. 6) Added simple currency/unit attributes for machine readability. 7) Ensured every element has both start and end tags and proper nesting, yielding well-formed XML."}
